            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and pat the&nbsp;<strong>mozzarella</strong>&nbsp;dry with kitchen paper</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>mozzarella</strong> in half lengthways&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>basil </strong>roughly,&nbsp;including the stalks</p>",
